{"tid":912901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"補選拉票　曾偉雄黃之鋒撞到正 街坊唔識分　禿鷹當基伯","createTime":"2018-11-23T04:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T06:33:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0072d5b7477b9d36cb0026fc18841a0dc55ff6","tid":912901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552703&d=2sUyXUM%2F3Pgi9fbUHNJmlQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=86a2786b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552703&h=8377c936\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552703</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月23日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：補選拉票　曾偉雄黃之鋒撞到正<br />\n街坊唔識分　禿鷹當基伯 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181123/large/a2001a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181123%2Flarge%2Fa2001a.gif&h=ad4d4b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n立法會九龍西補選今個星期日就舉行，民主派同建制派均出動知名人士喺最後關頭幫手拉票，其中建制派出動警務處前處長、有「禿鷹」之稱嘅曾偉雄，噚日朝喺黃埔為陳凱欣派單張拉票。最估唔到嘅係，企喺佢附近幫民主派代表李卓人拉票嘅人，竟然係當日佔領運動「雙學三子」之一嘅香港眾志黃之鋒，今次可謂「冤家路窄」撞到正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181123/large/1542905002_f488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181123%2Flarge%2F1542905002_f488.jpg&h=f6da6734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒話，俾曾偉雄拉咗咁多次，終於見到佢真人。黃之鋒fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：終於見到佢真人<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒噚日喺facebook話，噚日朝喺黃埔幫李卓人拉票時，發現現為全國政協的曾偉雄、建制派議員田北辰，均有現身為陳凱欣助選，黃之鋒話：「估唔到，連前警務處處長曾偉雄都落咗嚟，喺佢任內嘅警隊完全採用鐵腕管治，當年俾佢拉咗咁多次，終於見到佢真人。」黃之鋒又話，「不過睇嚟佢（曾偉雄）唔係好慣拉票，啲面部表情都有啲生硬，仲有街坊問我嗰個係咪馮檢基，可能髮型有啲似。」<br />\n<br />\n除咗黃之鋒一早現身為李卓人拉票，公民黨黨魁「岳少」楊岳橋，噚晚喺立法會開完大會後，亦再為李卓人助選落區，親力親為將李卓人的單張送入選民信箱，都算認真唔話得。補選其他候選人包括馮檢基、伍廸希和曾麗文。 <br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：列根號掛港區旗　同美國睇齊？ (李八方)"},{"pid":"d2330a19074c96f87ce66667621a053cbd97e642","tid":912901,"uid":14103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"俾佢拉左咁多次 終於見到佢真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf3f8519dc4b7ced85de0dca7d1aaf44f5cbc42","tid":912901,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"真心見到唔講未必認得到"},{"pid":"d2df8a59ff3af8331b57742328171c5a14fd5224","tid":912901,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NooMFEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNooMFEr.png&h=254c110f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec4138161215eaf3ab1215aaad8e2b02ba20a290","tid":912901,"uid":29880,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"泛民真係好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b2d858acfe47dfc32f345f5029ecfbd79feb92","tid":912901,"uid":56321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"以前班手足「暗角七警」仲上訴緊，仆街秃鷹未出過聲撐咁滯。當年靠雨革踩住班手足上位食完人血饅頭，宜家做咗政協，寧願走去企街幫個三九唔識七嘅助選立法會<br />\n<br />\n知唔知當年一句「你哋無做錯到」壯大班人個膽，害死幾多兄弟，遺禍幾深遠"},{"pid":"3adbbbc93dcb140282b3fc2b7af2ce780f1cefd6","tid":912901,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"當面屌佢老母啦"}]}